$ Graphviz - rankdir attribute
@ rankdir

The `rankdir` → tools/Graphviz/attributes[attribute] can be set to
  • `TB` (Top to Bottom)
  • `LR` (Left to Right)
  • `BT` (Bottom to Top)
  • `RL` (Right to Left)

? The `rankdir` attribute is only applicable for → tools/Graphviz/elems/graph[graphs] that are digraphs (`digraph { … }`).

sa:

  The value of `rankdir` determines the initial layout direction of → tools/Graphviz/elems/node[record based nodes].

  → tools/Graphviz/attributes[Graphviz attributes]

  → tools/Graphviz
